                     <interp inst="t17790404-23-verdict137" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder5s"></interp>
               GUILTY of stealing to the value of 4 s. 10 d
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the Second Middlesex Jury before Mr. DEPUTY RECORDER.</p>
